t shock proteins can stabilize or protect the structure of other proteins and specifically mutated HSPB1 was shown to bind to and stabilize microtubules and disturb microtubule dynamic instability (see below). [3]", "timestamp": "Mon Jun 08 15:14:55 +0000 2026"}